Field Detail

leafInfo

protected AutoDeleteMVBTree.LeafInfo leafInfo
LeafInfo for this node. This field is only used temporarily: it is only set when a new leaf node is created in the tree and only read when the new node is inserted into the container. At that point the field is set to null and is never used again.
